item.title: About Me
item.description: Hello there and welcome to my little corner! I’m a software crafter with a hybrid background in Software Engineering and Data Science with an MSc degree in AI and Databases. I’ve been working on fascinating tech projects around the world. If this sounds interesting do check my work journey on LinkedIn, I try to keep it up to date. At the moment, you can find me at Talkdesk as Engineering / Data Science Manager, taking part in a not so secret amazing project.
